    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// Pull company profile from earlier node\nconst profileRaw = $('Get Company Profile').first().json;\nconst profileFields = profileRaw.records?.[0]?.fields || {};\nconst profileText = Object.entries(profileFields)\n  .filter(([, v]) => v)\n  .map(([k, v]) => `${k}: ${v}`)\n  .join('\\n') || 'Financial consulting and audit company in Tashkent, Uzbekistan';\n\n// Get keywords for relevance filter\nconst keywords = (profileFields['Keywords'] || 'аудит,финансы,консалтинг,бухгалтер,audit,finance')\n  .toLowerCase().split(',').map(k => k.trim()).filter(Boolean);\n\n// Aggregate scraped content from all 6 sources\nconst items = $input.all();\nlet allContent = '';\n\nfor (const item of items) {\n  const markdown = item.json.data?.markdown || item.json.markdown || '';\n  const sourceUrl = item.json.data?.metadata?.url || item.json.url || '';\n  if (markdown.length > 200) {\n    allContent += `\\n\\n## Source: ${sourceUrl}\\n${markdown.slice(0, 3500)}`;\n  }\n}\n\n// Cap at 20k chars\nallContent = allContent.slice(0, 20000);\n\nconst prompt = `You are a tender analyst for a company in Tashkent, Uzbekistan.\n\nCOMPANY PROFILE:\n${profileText}\n\nSCRAPED TENDER CONTENT FROM 6 PLATFORMS:\n${allContent}\n\nExtract ALL tenders from the content and score each against the company profile.\n\nSCORING RULES:\n- missing or unclear budget → financial = 40-50 (NEVER 0)\n- matchPercent = compliance×0.4 + financial×0.2 + feasibility×0.25 + winChance×0.15\n- matchPercent ≥ 70 → recommendation = \"Подать заявку\"\n- matchPercent 40-69 → recommendation = \"Рассмотреть\"\n- matchPercent < 40 → recommendation = \"Пропустить\"\n\nReturn ONLY a valid JSON array (no markdown, no explanation):\n[\n  {\n    \"title\": \"string\",\n    \"organization\": \"string\",\n    \"budget\": \"string or null\",\n    \"deadline\": \"string or null\",\n    \"source\": \"URL string\",\n    \"platform\": \"platform name\",\n    \"matchPercent\": number 0-100,\n    \"recommendation\": \"Подать заявку|Рассмотреть|Пропустить\",\n    \"compliance\": number 0-100,\n    \"financial\": number 0-100,\n    \"feasibility\": number 0-100,\n    \"winChance\": number 0-100,\n    \"whyParticipate\": \"string\",\n    \"risks\": \"string\",\n    \"actionPlan\": \"string\",\n    \"riskLevel\": \"Низкий|Средний|Высокий\",\n    \"profitPotential\": \"Низкий|Средний|Высокий\"\n  }\n]\n\nExtract up to 15 most relevant tenders. Return [] if nothing found.`;\n\nreturn [{ json: { prompt, profileText } }];"
      },
